source : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBgMUB7xGcO0zn6g77BTt-0WvDeFC5vRt

Maven setup:

Download apache-maven-3.6.0-bin.zip (Binary zip archive) from https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi
Unzip where need to install example : 	D:\maven\apache-maven-3.6.0\bin
Set Enviroment Variables :
	set User variables for .... : Variable : M2_HOME ; Value : D:\maven\apache-maven-3.6.0
	set System variables : Path : D:\maven\apache-maven-3.6.0\bin

Check in command Prompt : mvn -version


Maven Project setup: 

Create a folder for the project
Open comment prompt & go to that dircory : example : cd folder-name 

write in command Prompt : mvn archetype:generate

find in command Prompt the type of project u want to create : 

For simple non web project search for example:  simple maven project , copy the serial number
		write in the command prompt & hit enter

write version number in command Prompt : example : 2 
& hit enter
write 'groupId' in command Prompt : example : com.growtogether
& hit enter
write 'artifactId' in command Prompt : example : maven-demo 
& hit enter
write 'version' in command Prompt : example : 1.0-SNAPSHOT
& hit enter 
write 'package' in command Prompt : example : com.growtogether.demos
& hit enter
write 'Y' in command Prompt & hit enter
